# Global Variables

#### toc

`\{{ toc }}` or `\{{> toc }}` or `\{{#toc [something]}}` 

#### toc sections/leves

``` yaml
---
title: YAML Front Matter
toc:
  level: 3
  section: Data
---
```
and

``` yaml
---
title: Configuration
toc:
  level: 3
  section: Data
---
```
and 

``` yaml
---
title: Data
toc:
  level: 2
---
```

and then in the partial: `toc.hbs`

``` hbs
---
toc:
  title: Table of Contents
---

\{{#markdown}}
# \{{toc.title}}

\{{toc}}
\{{/markdown}}
```

which would result in:

``` html
# Table of Contents

* [Data](path/to/data.md)
  - [Configuration](path/to/config.md)
  - [YAML Front Matter](path/to/front-matter.md)

```




